Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.51,0:03:26.10,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}浮生若夢　回眸幾何
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.61,0:03:37.69,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur4}你所製作的　玻璃飾品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.20,0:03:41.41,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur4}指尖一觸　寸心如割
