Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:53.34,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}愛　僅需一滴　臉頰便能浸潤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.34,0:03:56.26,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}心如刀絞　雨恨雲愁
