Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.32,0:23:13.53,Yuri004-ED-CHT-side-2,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}兩人一起　乘風破浪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.53,0:23:18.30,Yuri004-ED-CHT-side-2,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}這份堅不可摧的羈絆
